{"tid":2412500,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"沙嗲牛肉應該係咩味","createTime":"2021-02-18T05:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T15:51:57.000Z","uid":270966,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"086ae51d8befda3cf59386c2d290b96a6e821532","tid":2412500,"uid":270966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n放完新年假今日第一日返工返晏<br />\n見雖然已經過咗早餐時間<br />\n但好肚餓就照叫個$32沙嗲牛肉米食下<br />\n叫好外賣就坐定定拎張50蚊紙等俾錢啦<br />\n點知外賣一送到上嚟 話多謝你$35<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我心諗咁進取 一過年就加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要一下加幾蚊咁狼<br />\n唔理啦肚餓即刻俾錢坐低開餐先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n滿心歡喜有嘢食 一打開 <br />\n我dklm!(省略感歎號x1000000000)<br />\n點解會有洋蔥甜椒豆豉㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係叫沙嗲牛肉米喎<br />\n湯粉麵嗰隻 唔係沙嗲粉絲煲喎<br />\n是咪炒錯咗豉椒牛肉過我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想跑落去捉住廚房條友幫佢開個靚年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜要搞到紅紅綠綠咁色彩繽紛先<br />\n啲椒同洋蔥就好似紅綠燈咁不斷衝擊我嘅視覺<br />\n好想成碗倒咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但又真係太肚餓<br />\n最後唯有抱住懷疑忐忑嘅心情食埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頂成碗粉完全冇沙嗲嘅花生香味<br />\n只係得洋蔥青紅椒同豆豉味充斥住我個鼻同口腔<br />\n我食完碗粉之後嘅心情好複雜<br />\n唔係Monday都俾佢搞到個人好blue<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是咪我嘅問題我見識少呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁大個人第一次食咁難食嘅沙嗲牛肉米<br />\n亦都係第一次見有人會落洋蔥青紅椒<br />\n成碗變咗豆豉味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食到我懷疑人生<br />\n正正常常唔係應該係花生味嗰隻嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下咁多位巴打絲打食開邊隻味係正常？<br />\n正常茶記花生味沙嗲 係唔會落豆豉嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加洋蔥甜椒嘅豉椒味囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d81dc6ce3d7fb6627e882fa966f9b02feaecba","tid":2412500,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"洋蔥"},{"pid":"d67a1f766b39ab20045161ab788a9fbc9b30d1af","tid":2412500,"uid":251696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"086ae51d8befda3cf59386c2d290b96a6e821532","tid":2412500,"uid":270966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n放完新年假今日第一日返工返晏<br />\n見雖然已經過咗早餐時間<br />\n但好肚餓就照叫個$32沙嗲牛肉米食下<br />\n叫好外賣就坐定定拎張50蚊紙等俾錢啦<br />\n點知外賣一送到上嚟 話多謝你$35<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我心諗咁進取 一過年就加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要一下加幾蚊咁狼<br />\n唔理啦肚餓即刻俾錢坐低開餐先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n滿心歡喜有嘢食 一打開 <br />\n我dklm!(省略感歎號x1000000000)<br />\n點解會有洋蔥甜椒豆豉㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係叫沙嗲牛肉米喎<br />\n湯粉麵嗰隻 唔係沙嗲粉絲煲喎<br />\n是咪炒錯咗豉椒牛肉過我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想跑落去捉住廚房條友幫佢開個靚年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜要搞到紅紅綠綠咁色彩繽紛先<br />\n啲椒同洋蔥就好似紅綠燈咁不斷衝擊我嘅視覺<br />\n好想成碗倒咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但又真係太肚餓<br />\n最後唯有抱住懷疑忐忑嘅心情食埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頂成碗粉完全冇沙嗲嘅花生香味<br />\n只係得洋蔥青紅椒同豆豉味充斥住我個鼻同口腔<br 